d on a sleek, rotating pedestal, highlighting the technology and design, surrounded by holographic projections of translated text in various languages, suggesting advanced functionality and user-friendly interface.","name":"Sofía Pereira","role":"Ejecutiva de Ventas","detail":"Las gafas han transformado mi forma de negociar con clientes extranjeros. La comunicación es instantánea y sin malentendidos."},{"avatar":"https://txcdn-prod-a1art.xiaopiu.com/assets/images/app_1925013562074480641/1925013562078674945/1ccbfcdf-ccf8-4210-b1ef-36172a4e7b11.jpeg?oldPrompt=A split-screen showing a before-and-after scenario: one side with people struggling to communicate, the other side with them communicating effortlessly using the translation glasses, emphasizing the benefit of bridging language barriers in a professional setting.","name":"Javier Torres","role":"Consultor Internacional","detail":"Viajo constantemente por trabajo y las gafas son mi mejor aliado. Me permiten comunicarme con confianza en cualquier país."}]}}

